---
/**
 * Germany Hero section — modern Astro component
 * Deep dark slate background, glowing radial blobs, checklist, countdown, and active HubSpot form.
 */
---

<section class="hero relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0A0F1E] text-white pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-24 max-md:pt-28 max-md:pb-16" id="hero">
  <!-- Glow effects -->
  <div class="absolute -top-[200px] -right-[200px] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,87,255,0.18)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-[150px] -left-[150px] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(137,110,196,0.12)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1160px] px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
    
    <!-- Hero Left -->
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[rgba(0,87,255,0.18)] border border-[rgba(0,87,255,0.35)] text-[#93b8ff] text-xs font-semibold px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 tracking-wider uppercase">
        <span class="text-sm">🇩🇪</span> Germany Mandate
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight mb-6 font-head">
        <span class="text-white/50 line-through decoration-white/30 decoration-2">2027 mandate.</span><br />
        <span class="text-[#5b9bff] italic font-medium">ViDA 2030</span> is the real story.
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-[540px]">
        Most German finance leaders are buying a tool for the 2027 deadline. They'll be buying a second one in 2029 when ViDA cross-border reporting goes live. <strong class="text-white font-semibold">ClearTax is built for both.</strong> One platform. One integration. Every European mandate, current and future.
      </p>

      <ul class="list-none p-0 m-0 mb-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3.5 text-sm lg:text-base text-white/85">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
          <span>2025 receive & 2027 issue — covered Day 1, no rebuild required</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3.5 text-sm lg:text-base text-white/85">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
          <span>ViDA 2030 cross-border DRR and single VAT registration — already in the platform</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3.5 text-sm lg:text-base text-white/85">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
          <span>Same API handles 40+ country mandates. One vendor, one contract, one roadmap</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/50 text-xs lg:text-sm">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
          <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#0057FF] rounded-full opacity-70 animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#0057FF] rounded-full opacity-70 animate-pulse delay-75"></span>
          <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#0057FF] rounded-full opacity-70 animate-pulse delay-150"></span>
        </div>
        <span>Listed on VeR · Trusted by 100+ EU enterprises</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Right -->
    <aside class="hero-form bg-white text-[#111827] rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] w-full scroll-mt-28" id="heroForm">
      <div class="hf-fields">
        <!-- Countdown Banner -->
        <div class="countdown bg-[#0A0F1E] text-white rounded-xl p-3.5 mb-6 text-center border border-white/10" aria-label="Countdown to German B2B e-invoicing issue mandate">
          <div class="text-[10px] lg:text-xs font-bold text-white/60 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-head">Mandatory B2B · 1 Jan 2027</div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-1.5 items-end" id="cdGrid" aria-live="polite">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none tabular-nums" id="cd-days">—</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mt-1">Days</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none tabular-nums" id="cd-hrs">—</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mt-1">Hrs</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none tabular-nums" id="cd-min">—</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mt-1">Min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none tabular-nums" id="cd-sec">—</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mt-1">Sec</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-extrabold text-[#0A0F1E] mb-1.5 font-head tracking-tight leading-snug">Book a 20-minute demo</h3>
        <p class="text-xs lg:text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 leading-relaxed">German-speaking specialists. 2025 → 2027 → ViDA 2030 on one platform.</p>

        <!-- HubSpot Form Mount -->
        <div id="hero-hubspot-form" class="hs-form-wrap"></div>
      </div>
    </aside>

  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  // Countdown to German B2B e-invoicing issue mandate: 1 Jan 2027 (CET)
  (() => {
    const deadline = new Date('2027-01-01T00:00:00+01:00').getTime();
    const el = {
      d: document.getElementById('cd-days'),
      h: document.getElementById('cd-hrs'),
      m: document.getElementById('cd-min'),
      s: document.getElementById('cd-sec'),
    };
    if (!el.d) return;
    function pad(n) { return String(n).padStart(2, '0'); }
    function tick() {
      const now = Date.now();
      let diff = Math.max(0, deadline - now);
      const days = Math.floor(diff / 86400000); diff -= days * 86400000;
      const hours = Math.floor(diff / 3600000); diff -= hours * 3600000;
      const mins = Math.floor(diff / 60000); diff -= mins * 60000;
      const secs = Math.floor(diff / 1000);
      el.d.textContent = pad(days);
      el.h.textContent = pad(hours);
      el.m.textContent = pad(mins);
      el.s.textContent = pad(secs);
    }
    tick();
    setInterval(tick, 1000);
  })();

  // HubSpot form embed with URL parameters auto-prefill
  (() => {
    const initForm = () => {
      if (window.hbspt && window.hbspt.forms) {
        window.hbspt.forms.create({
          portalId: "245744706",
          formId: "71533f54-577f-4f7a-8df9-f1b9600026c8",
          region: "na2",
          target: "#hero-hubspot-form",
          onFormReady: function($form) {
            const formEl = ($form && $form[0]) ? $form[0] : $form;
            if (formEl && formEl.querySelector) {
              const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
              const utms = ['utm_source', 'utm_medium', 'utm_campaign', 'utm_term', 'utm_content'];
              utms.forEach(utm => {
                const value = urlParams.get(utm);
                if (value) {
                  const input = formEl.querySelector('input[name="' + utm + '"]');
                  if (input) {
                    input.value = value;
                  }
                }
              });
            }
          }
        });
      }
    };

    if (document.readyState === "loading") {
      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", initForm);
    } else {
      initForm();
    }
  })();
</script>

<style is:global>
  /* Premium overrides for HubSpot Form */
  .hs-form-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 380px;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap form {
    display: flex !important;
    flex-direction: column !important;
    gap: 16px !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-field {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-field > label {
    display: block !important;
    font-size: 12px !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    color: #111827 !important;
    margin-bottom: 4px !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-field > label .hs-form-required {
    color: #dc2626 !important;
    margin-left: 2px !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="text"],
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="email"],
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="tel"],
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="number"],
  .hs-form-wrap select,
  .hs-form-wrap textarea {
    width: 100% !important;
    border-radius: 8px !important;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB !important;
    background-color: #ffffff !important;
    padding: 10px 14px !important;
    font-size: 14px !important;
    color: #111827 !important;
    outline: none !important;
    transition: all 0.2s ease !important;
    box-sizing: border-box !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap input:focus,
  .hs-form-wrap select:focus,
  .hs-form-wrap textarea:focus {
    border-color: #0057FF !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 87, 255, 0.12) !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap textarea {
    min-height: 80px !important;
    resize: vertical !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap select {
    appearance: auto !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap fieldset {
    max-width: none !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    display: flex !important;
    flex-direction: row !important;
    gap: 12px !important;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hs-form-wrap fieldset {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      gap: 16px !important;
    }
  }
  .hs-form-wrap fieldset .hs-form-field {
    flex: 1 !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap fieldset .input {
    margin-right: 0 !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-booleancheckbox label,
  .hs-form-wrap .legal-consent-container label {
    display: flex !important;
    align-items: flex-start !important;
    gap: 8px !important;
    font-size: 11.5px !important;
    color: #6B7280 !important;
    line-height: 1.5 !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    cursor: pointer !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-booleancheckbox label a,
  .hs-form-wrap .legal-consent-container label a {
    color: #0057FF !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    text-decoration: underline !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="checkbox"] {
    margin-top: 3px !important;
    flex-shrink: 0 !important;
    accent-color: #0057FF !important;
    width: 14px !important;
    height: 14px !important;
    cursor: pointer !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-submit {
    margin-top: 8px !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="submit"],
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-button {
    width: 100% !important;
    background: #0057FF !important;
    color: white !important;
    padding: 12px !important;
    border-radius: 8px !important;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
    font-size: 14px !important;
    border: none !important;
    cursor: pointer !important;
    font-family: inherit !important;
    transition: all 0.15s ease !important;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 87, 255, 0.15) !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap input[type="submit"]:hover,
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-button:hover {
    background: #0041cc !important;
    transform: translateY(-1px) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 87, 255, 0.25) !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-error-msgs {
    list-style: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 4px 0 0 !important;
    font-size: 11px !important;
    color: #dc2626 !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-error-msg {
    color: #dc2626 !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap .submitted-message {
    background: #e8effe !important;
    color: #0057FF !important;
    padding: 16px !important;
    border-radius: 8px !important;
    font-size: 14px !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    text-align: center !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 87, 255, 0.15) !important;
  }
  .hs-form-wrap fieldset:has([class*="hs_utm_"]),
  .hs-form-wrap .hs-form-field[style*="display: none"] {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>
